ragnarok-installer (01-2) stable; urgency=medium

  * New tools: setlocale, setkb, settz. These can be used during
    chroot-style installs to properly and quickly set up the locale,
    timezone and keymap.

 -- Ian LeCorbeau <I-LeCorbeau@protonmail.com>  Sun, 01 Oct 2024 15:33:32 -0400

ragnarok-installer (01-1) stable; urgency=medium

  * Use the '_installer' user for commands that need to
    be run without root privileges.

